## 4 · Command Reference

Base: `node bin/jira-cli.mjs <cmd> [args] [--json] [--limit N] [--no-sync]`

### Reads

| cmd         | args             | Purpose                       |
| ----------- | ---------------- | ----------------------------- |
| `my`        | `[custom JQL]`   | My open tasks (default 20)    |
| `sprint`    | `[custom JQL]`   | Current sprint issues         |
| `get`       | `KEY`            | Single issue detail           |
| `batch`     | `KEY KEY …`      | Multiple issues, one API call |
| `subtasks`  | `PARENT-KEY`     | Children of a parent          |
| `search`    | `"JQL"`          | Custom JQL query              |
| `me`        |                  | Current user info             |
| `recent`    |                  | Recent Confluence pages       |
| `spaces`    |                  | List Confluence spaces        |
| `find-user` | `"display name"` | Look up accountId by name     |

### Writes

| cmd              | args                                                    | Purpose                |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| `create`         | `"Summary" [--type Story\|Bug\|Task] [--priority High]` | Create top-level issue |
| `create-subtask` | `PARENT-KEY "Summary" [accountId]`                      | New subtask            |
| `assign`         | `KEY [KEY …] accountId`                                 | Assign issues          |
| `transition`     | `KEY [KEY …] "Status Name"`                             | Change status          |
| `update`         | `KEY '{"field":"value"}'`                               | Edit fields            |
| `comment`        | `KEY "text"`                                            | Add comment            |

### Cache

| cmd    | Purpose                                   |
| ------ | ----------------------------------------- |
| `sync` | Rebuild `sprint.md` + `.sprint-meta.json` |

