## 6 · Error Handling

| Error                    | What to tell the user                                                                             |
| ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 401 Unauthorized         | "Your Jira token may have expired. Ask your admin to regenerate it."                              |
| 404 Not Found            | "I couldn't find that issue. Double-check the key."                                               |
| Network error            | "I can't reach Jira right now. Check your internet connection and try again."                     |
| No transitions available | "That issue can't be moved to [status] from its current state. Here are the available options: …" |
| Empty results            | "No results found. Want me to try a broader search?"                                              |

Never show raw HTTP status codes or API error payloads to the user.

